originalText.text:
I had a great experience working with Josh. Josh helped me to buy a condo in the Upper West Side.

Right from the beginning, Josh was very responsive and knowledgeable when I contacted him about my desire to purchase a condo in the area. He took the time to understand my needs and preferences and provided me with an array of properties that fit my criteria.

Throughout the process, Josh was always available to answer my questions, provide guidance, and offer his expertise. He was patient and understanding, and he never pressured me into making a decision. Instead, he listened to my concerns and helped me navigate the complex world of real estate with ease.
When I found the perfect condo, Josh was instrumental in negotiating a fair price and ensuring that all the necessary paperwork was completed in a timely manner. He also connected me with other professionals, such as a mortgage broker and an attorney, who were equally helpful and professional.

Overall, my experience working with Josh was excellent. His knowledge of the Upper West Side real estate market, his professionalism, and his commitment to his clients are second to none. I would highly recommend Josh to anyone looking to buy or sell a property in the area.

originalText.text: Josh is one of New York's top brokers, and I was lucky to be able to work with him. He is extremely communicative and attentive to every step of the process, passionate and dedicated to his clients. You will feel like his top priority until the deal is done and, even after, he will be in touch to make sure you are happy. It is the sort of working relationship where you feel in capable hands, as well as making a long-term contact, even a friend, since he has such a personal and thoughtful touch in business. You will be glad you went with Josh for all of your real estate needs. I have referred my own friends to him as well and you will likely find yourself doing the same in order to share the wealth.
